narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Awesome class with tons of work, but if you want to learn Chinese well, definitely take this class (you probably have to take it anyway if you started with CHNS 110). All the professors are really good at teaching, so you'll make a ton of progress.
I would only recommend CHNS 120 for students really interested in learning Chinese and invested in working 2-3 hours a night.
A lot of work but a good and predictable course
